  <bodyText><![CDATA[<div class="g12">
<div class="white_box_shadow"><img src="/media/13086380/inghams-landing-page.jpg" alt="Black Friday Sale 2020" /></div>
<p><strong><span class="geolocation-title">Save £50 per person on all summer holidays when you book between 27th November - 1st December.</span></strong></p>
<p><em>This year, we're offering you the chance to take <a data-udi="umb://document/689ff8bd3fd047c1ac987e14b42fb86b" href="/{localLink:umb://document/689ff8bd3fd047c1ac987e14b42fb86b}" title="Black Friday Deals">£50pp off any Inghams summer holiday</a>. Just book between Friday 27th November 00:00 and Tuesday 1st December 22:59 to take advantage of our Black Friday saving. T&amp;Cs apply.</em></p>
<p><em>Whether you're hoping to spend a week sunbathing in Sardinia or a weekend walking through the Austrian Alps, we'll take £50pp off your holiday cost this Black Friday, no strings attached. This offer is valid on all dates, all destinations and all types of holiday this summer - even tours. </em></p>
<p><em>There are no exclusions which means this year's Black Friday deal can even be combined with our £75 low deposit offer. </em></p>
<p><em>We all deserve something lovely to look forward to next year, so why not make the most of these seasonal savings and get something in the diary for summer 2021? With Inghams, you're <a data-udi="umb://document/fa72be9e45bc442089252c6a18a0d2ae" href="/{localLink:umb://document/fa72be9e45bc442089252c6a18a0d2ae}" title="In Safe Hands">In Safe Hands</a> with our Covid-19 refund promise.</em></p>
<p><strong>Discover our favourite summer 2021 deals below.</strong></p>
<div class="data-grid" style="float: center;">
<table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" class="tablet-button" style="height: 20px; width: 300px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;">
