</table>
</div>
<div class="data-grid" style="float: center;"></div>
<div class="data-grid" style="float: center;"><strong>Terms and Conditions</strong></div>
<ul>
<li>£50 per person discount applies to adult prices only.</li>
<li>Prices shown on website include the discount.</li>
<li>Book by Tuesday 1 December 22:59</li>
<li>Discount not valid on flight-only or accommodation-only bookings.</li>
<li>Applies to new bookings only and cannot be added retrospectively. Subject to availability.</li>
<li>Can be combined with existing offers.</li>
<li>No options can be held for holidays taking this promotion.</li>
<li>Prices and offers are subject to change and can be withdrawn at any time.</li>
<li>Applicable on all summer holidays (Lakes &amp; Mountains, Italy &amp; Tours)</li>
<li>Valid on all package holidays meeting the above criteria which include flights, transfers and accommodation.</li>
</ul>
